Eamonn Holmes, 62, shared a lovely photograph with his 31-year-old daughter, Becca. The duo attended Royal Ascot 2022 at Ascot at Ascot Racecourse earlier this week.  In a snap shared to Instagram, the father-daughter duo smiled as Eamonn took a selfie.The GB News presenter looked dapper in a grey top hat with matching waistcoat.He paired the look with a black blazer, grey striped trousers and yellow tie.Becca looked gorgeous in a navy blue dress with a fascinator to match.After sharing the snap, Eamonn was inundated with complimentary messages, including from his wife Ruth Langsford.The Loose Women star gushed: “What a gorgeous pair!” And added two heart emojis.